coding_questions.title: Maximum Subarray
coding_questions.description: Given an integer array, find the maximum contiguous subarray (a subarray with the largest sum).
coding_questions.constraints: The input array will have at least one element and at most 1000 elements. Each element will be an integer between -1000 and 1000.

coding_questions.title: Binary Search
coding_questions.description: Given a sorted array and a target value, find the index of the target value in the array using binary search.
coding_questions.constraints: The input array will have at least one element and at most 1000 elements. Each element will be an integer between -1000 and 1000. The target value will be an integer between -1000 and 1000.
